theme_override_colors/font_color = Color(0.88, 0.88, 0.93, 1.0)
theme_override_font_sizes/font_size = 13
size_flags_horizontal = 3
autowrap_mode = 3
text = "OBJECTIVE
Survive 14 weeks of university life at UM and pass the final exam!

HOW TO PLAY
Each week, walk around campus and enter buildings to interact with them.
Once you are done, click \"Next Week\" to advance to the next week.
Random events may occur each week — stay prepared!

YOUR STATS
GPA        Academic score. Must stay above 2.0.
Stress     Pressure level (0-100). Hits 100 = Game Over!
Energy     Stamina (0-100). Drops to 0 = Game Over!
Money      Budget in RM. Goes below -RM50 = Game Over!
Social     Friendships and connections.

CAMPUS LOCATIONS
Faculty          Attend class.         GPA up, Energy down.
Library          Study quietly.        GPA up, slight Stress up.
Cafeteria        Eat a meal.           Energy up, Money down.
Sports Centre    Exercise.             Stress down, Social up.
Club Room        Club activity.        Social up, small GPA drop.
Kolej Kediaman   Rest in your room.    Energy up, Stress down.

ENDINGS (7 TYPES)
Gym Freak            Visit Sports Centre 8 or more times
Campus Celebrity     Social > 90
Millionaire Student  Money > RM 150
Dean List            GPA >= 3.7 and Stress <= 50
Burnout              Stress >= 80 at semester end
Academic Probation   GPA < 2.0 at semester end
Balanced Student     Survive without hitting any extreme

TIPS
- Visit Faculty every week to keep your GPA healthy.
- Use Sports Centre and Cafeteria to manage Stress and Energy.
- Keep all stats balanced for the best ending!"

